page.title: 11Biography
page.content: {A day in the life of Guy WentworthWood I woke up at forty_seven minutes past seven.I went downstairs and had my breakfast my cereal was 'START' ,I also had some toast.After my breakfast I watched television for half an hour then I dressed.At ten o'clock I went with my dad to the Exhaust Centre to get a new exhaust for the car.After that I picked up my sister from ballet class.Then I went home and had my lunch which was a salmon batch.In the afternoon I playedwith my plastercine and made an aeroplane.At four o'clock my friends came for tea.It was a buffet.We had crisps,sausage,lettuce, carrots and eggs.After tea I played outside in the street.Then I came in and played on my computer.After that I watched some more televsion and I went to bed at half past eight.....
